// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2588 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: dd174011-6723-5f0e-8c41-f50f445b3b99

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.10*")
